snippet: The three-time world champion Mao Asada won the Cup of China in Beijing, completing a successful return to the Grand Prix series after taking a year off.
abstract: Japanese figure skater Mao Asada wins women's event at Cup of China in Beijing.
lead_paragraph: The three-time world champion Mao Asada won the Cup of China in Beijing, completing a successful return to the Grand Prix series after taking a year off.

headline.main: Asada Returns From Year’s Absence With Win
